        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" , "Rationale: localisation of NR1 in presynapse using immuno EM.\n\n22/11/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: For preembedding immuno electron microscopy, a 24-day-old Wistar rat was anesthetized with pentobarbital (60 mg/kg) and intracardially perfused with 4% PFA and 0.1% glutaraldehyde in PBS. After dissection, the cerebellum was kept overnight at 4 °C in 4% PFA. Vibratome saggital sections (100" ;
